Comment.val: /*Program that assembles the CombiOrderCreate xml message to be send to Fintegrator. */

Text.val: Virtuals to write the XML message
Record for CombiOrderNew not found --> Error
clOrdID --> Manditory filled with clOrdId from leg 1
executingFirm --> Optional, can't be filled with data
clearingFirm --> Optional, can't be filled with data
clearingAccount --> Optional, can't be filled with data
investorID --> Optional, can't be filled with data
enteringFirm --> Optional, can't be filled with data
originationTrader --> Optional, can't be filled with data
originationFirm --> Optional, can't be filled with data
symbol --> Optional, the symbol fields in the legs are filled
securitySubType --> Manditory, Be aware do not trim!
underlyingID --> Optional, but when applied id en sourceID are both manditory
leg --> Manditory min and max 2 legs
securityID --> Optional, but when applied id and sourceID are manditory
securityAltID --> Optional, can't be filled with data
putOrCall --> Optional (value 0 is a valid value, so no check on putOrCall <> 0)
securityID --> Optional, but when applied id and sourceID are both manditory
securityAltID --> Optional, can't be filled with data
putOrCall --> Optional (value 0 is a valid value, so no check on putOrCall <> 0)
locateReqd --> Optional, can't be filled with data
timeInForce --> Optional (value 0 is a valid value, so no check on timeInForce<>0)
coveredOrUncovered --> Optional, can't be filled with data
origTime --> Optional, can't be filled with data
preOpenFlag --> Optional, can't be filled with data, N/A
clientType --> Optional (NB in EP+ is this the column RelationKind)
